1. Element : start and end with tag <h1></h1>,p, br
  Attributes : before the "equal to sign" . src, img
  Entity : with & symbol : &nbsp, &lt, &gt
  
2. CSS white color :
rgb - rgb(255,255,255)
hexa representation : #FFFFFF
HSL - (0,100,100)

3. Change state of the link : active, normal, hover, visited.

5. change font on website 
- By adding style tag on head, and all css will be between the style tag
- By adding an external file, and linking it to the html file  
- By creating an inline style
 

6. Text horizontal :text-align: center
   Text vertical : vertical-align: text-top;
   Text uppercase : text-transform:uppercase;
   Add strike : text-decoration: line-through
   
